I"c<h3 id="create-a-remote-branch-feature-1">create a remote branch feature-1</h3>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c"># syntax</span>
git checkout <span class="nt">-b</span> &lt;branch_name&gt;
git push &lt;remote_name&gt; &lt;branch_name&gt;

<span class="c"># example</span>
git checkout <span class="nt">-b</span> feature-1
git push origin feature-1
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="delete-a-remote-branch-feature-2">delete a remote branch feature-2</h3>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c"># syntax</span>
git push &lt;remote_name&gt; <span class="nt">--delete</span> &lt;branch_name&gt;

<span class="c"># example</span>
git push origin <span class="nt">--delete</span> feature-2
</code></pre></div></div>
